Crunch←{
  x←⟨⟩
  IsString◶{
    x∾↩⥊¨∾∘("¯∞N"⊸(⊑⊐)◶"-"‿"inf"‿"n"‿⥊¨•Repr)⍟(2≠•Type)¨⥊𝕩
